{"tid":791290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【十姑娘病逝】曾戀上堂弟何鴻章 婚外情誕下兩子女","createTime":"2018-08-23T16:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T23:32:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd15c2ef02e05f5ab27b448188eaeb69562e7ba","tid":791290,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"「十姑娘」何婉琪於1946年嫁給麥志偉，可是與年輕3歲、堂弟何鴻章發生婚外情，兩人早於1941年何東的結婚紀念舞會上一見鍾情，至1953年二人在港重遇時，愛火一發不可收拾，兩年後十姑娘為何鴻章誕下私生子麥舜銘(何東舜銘)，之後又為對方誕下麥慧玉。<br />\n<br />\n十姑娘與何鴻章的關係至1974年中斷，麥舜銘(何東舜銘)更於2001年6月公開何鴻章是其生父的身分。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/000831_dbbb19c919c8ced66f9ac59996197890.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F000831_dbbb19c919c8ced66f9ac59996197890.png&h=e1674a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1535027123352&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1535027123352%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180823&d=RzP3LsgGeiXY4iqKetPgmi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7698911e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1535027123352%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180823&h=0b492dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1535027123352&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180823</a>"},{"pid":"3bab029ba4f47b39599f1873e24e2d7fea1d912c","tid":791290,"uid":10101,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"亂倫？"},{"pid":"2a0383fafd9df2d77b3e18edac1485dbc31057e9","tid":791290,"uid":13504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"XXX 同XXX 有無造過愛？"},{"pid":"ba17f03d6f3170bcb12d37fda052fd391326a676","tid":791290,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:12:32.000Z"